<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { title, description }) %>
</head>
<body class="bg-page text-text-primary font-body antialiased overflow-x-hidden">
  <canvas id="dot-grid" class="fixed inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
  <div id="cursor-glow" class="fixed w-[320px] h-[320px] rounded-full pointer-events-none z-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,130,246,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(-50%, -50%);" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <main class="relative z-10 pt-20">
    <section class="py-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-accent/20 bg-accent/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">AI Mastermind</span>
        <h1 class="mt-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-black tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">A weekly conversation about what is actually working with AI.</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
          Not a webinar and not a generic workshop. This is a smaller, practical conversation for builders and business owners sharing what they are testing, building, and learning in real time.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-border-subtle bg-card px-6 py-4 text-left">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-accent shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"></rect><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line></svg>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary">Wednesdays</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">3pm Bucharest, 8pm Bali, 8am New York</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10">
          <a href="#signup-form" class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>Join the Mastermind</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="glass-card p-10 lg:p-14 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">What to expect</h2>
          <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3 text-left">
            <div>
              <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/15 text-accent">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v2m6.364 1.636-1.414 1.414M21 12h-2M6.343 6.343 4.929 7.757M4 12H2m4.343 5.657-1.414 1.414M12 19v2m5.657-3.343 1.414 1.414"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"></circle></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-display font-bold">A real topic</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Each session starts with something concrete: a demo, a build, a workflow, or a useful shift in the AI landscape.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/15 text-accent">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 0 0-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 0 1 5.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 0 1 9.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0z"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-display font-bold">Shared learning</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Members bring what they are exploring, what is stuck, and what is creating traction so the conversation stays grounded in experience.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/15 text-accent">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-display font-bold">Open level</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Whether you are already building agents or still figuring out where AI fits, the room is designed to be useful rather than performative.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="glass-card p-8 lg:p-10" data-tilt>
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Who It Is For</span>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Builders experimenting with AI workflows, agents, or internal automation</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Business owners trying to understand where AI creates actual leverage</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Operators who want practical conversations instead of high-level hype</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="glass-card p-8 lg:p-10" data-tilt>
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Current Format</span>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Weekly live session</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Cosmo opens with a topic, build, or useful pattern</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>Discussion expands into questions, experiments, and lessons from the group</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm lg:pb-section">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <div class="glass-card p-10 lg:p-14">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">Interested?</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">Want in on the next session?</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            If this feels relevant, fill out the signup form below. Once the backend is wired, this will route to a thank-you page and the calendar flow.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="#signup-form" class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>Go to Signup Form</a>
            <a href="https://calendly.com/cosminlungu/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex rounded-xl border border-border-subtle px-8 py-4 text-text-secondary font-semibold transition-colors hover:border-text-muted hover:text-text-primary">Book a Call</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="signup-form" class="pb-section-sm lg:pb-section">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="glass-card p-8 lg:p-10">
          <div class="max-w-2xl mb-10">
            <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">Signup</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">Join the AI Mastermind</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
              Fill this out to join the list for upcoming sessions. Your details are stored for mastermind signup and session communication.
            </p>
          </div>

          <form id="mastermind-signup-form" class="space-y-6" novalidate>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label for="first-name" class="block text-sm font-body font-medium text-text-secondary mb-2">First Name <span class="text-red-400">*</span></label>
                <input type="text" id="first-name" name="first_name" class="w-full bg-page border border-border-subtle rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-primary text-sm placeholder:text-text-muted focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent transition-colors" placeholder="Alex">
                <p class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-1 hidden" data-error="first_name"></p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="last-name" class="block text-sm font-body font-medium text-text-secondary mb-2">Last Name <span class="text-red-400">*</span></label>
                <input type="text" id="last-name" name="last_name" class="w-full bg-page border border-border-subtle rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-primary text-sm placeholder:text-text-muted focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent transition-colors" placeholder="Morgan">
                <p class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-1 hidden" data-error="last_name"></p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label for="mastermind-email" class="block text-sm font-body font-medium text-text-secondary mb-2">Email <span class="text-red-400">*</span></label>
                <input type="email" id="mastermind-email" name="email" autocomplete="email" class="w-full bg-page border border-border-subtle rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-primary text-sm placeholder:text-text-muted focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent transition-colors" placeholder="alex@company.com" required>
                <p class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-1 hidden" data-error="email"></p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="mastermind-website" class="block text-sm font-body font-medium text-text-secondary mb-2">Website <span class="text-text-muted">(optional)</span></label>
                <input type="url" id="mastermind-website" name="website" class="w-full bg-page border border-border-subtle rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-primary text-sm placeholder:text-text-muted focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent transition-colors" placeholder="https://yourcompany.com">
                <p class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-1 hidden" data-error="website"></p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label for="mastermind-role" class="block text-sm font-body font-medium text-text-secondary mb-2">Role <span class="text-red-400">*</span></label>
                <select id="mastermind-role" name="role" class="w-full bg-page border border-border-subtle rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-primary text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent transition-colors">
                  <option value="">Select your role</option>
                  <option>Builder</option>
                  <option>Business Owner</option>
                  <option>Operator</option>
                  <option>Both</option>
                </select>
                <p class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-1 hidden" data-error="role"></p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="mastermind-experience" class="block text-sm font-body font-medium text-text-secondary mb-2">AI Experience <span class="text-red-400">*</span></label>
                <select id="mastermind-experience" name="ai_experience" class="w-full bg-page border border-border-subtle rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-primary text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent transition-colors">
                  <option value="">Select your level</option>
                  <option>Beginner</option>
                  <option>Intermediate</option>
                  <option>Advanced</option>
                </select>
                <p class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-1 hidden" data-error="ai_experience"></p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="block text-sm font-body font-medium text-text-secondary mb-3">Goals <span class="text-red-400">*</span></label>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
                <label class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="goals" value="Learn" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-border-subtle bg-page text-accent focus:ring-accent">
                  <span>Learn</span>
                </label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="goals" value="Share" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-border-subtle bg-page text-accent focus:ring-accent">
                  <span>Share</span>
                </label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="goals" value="Network" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-border-subtle bg-page text-accent focus:ring-accent">
                  <span>Network</span>
                </label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="goals" value="Get feedback" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-border-subtle bg-page text-accent focus:ring-accent">
                  <span>Get feedback</span>
                </label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="goals" value="Explore tools" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-border-subtle bg-page text-accent focus:ring-accent">
                  <span>Explore tools</span>
                </label>
                <label class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="goals" value="Other" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-border-subtle bg-page text-accent focus:ring-accent">
                  <span>Other</span>
                </label>
              </div>
              <p class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-1 hidden" data-error="goals"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="mastermind-timezone" class="block text-sm font-body font-medium text-text-secondary mb-2">Timezone <span class="text-red-400">*</span></label>
              <select id="mastermind-timezone" name="timezone" class="w-full bg-page border border-border-subtle rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-primary text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent transition-colors">
                <option value="">Select your timezone</option>
                <optgroup label="North America">
                  <option value="America/New_York">Eastern Time - New York (GMT-4)</option>
                  <option value="America/Chicago">Central Time - Chicago (GMT-5)</option>
                  <option value="America/Denver">Mountain Time - Denver (GMT-6)</option>
                  <option value="America/Los_Angeles">Pacific Time - Los Angeles (GMT-7)</option>
                  <option value="America/Toronto">Toronto (GMT-4)</option>
                  <option value="America/Vancouver">Vancouver (GMT-7)</option>
                  <option value="Pacific/Honolulu">Honolulu (GMT-10)</option>
                </optgroup>
                <optgroup label="Europe">
                  <option value="Europe/London">London (GMT+1)</option>
                  <option value="Europe/Berlin">Berlin (GMT+2)</option>
                  <option value="Europe/Paris">Paris (GMT+2)</option>
                  <option value="Europe/Bucharest">Bucharest (GMT+3)</option>
                  <option value="Europe/Madrid">Madrid (GMT+2)</option>
                  <option value="Europe/Rome">Rome (GMT+2)</option>
                  <option value="Europe/Moscow">Moscow (GMT+3)</option>
                </optgroup>
                <optgroup label="Asia">
                  <option value="Asia/Dubai">Dubai (GMT+4)</option>
                  <option value="Asia/Kolkata">Mumbai (GMT+5:30)</option>
                  <option value="Asia/Bangkok">Bangkok (GMT+7)</option>
                  <option value="Asia/Shanghai">Beijing (GMT+8)</option>
                  <option value="Asia/Singapore">Singapore (GMT+8)</option>
                  <option value="Asia/Makassar">Bali (GMT+8)</option>
                  <option value="Asia/Tokyo">Tokyo (GMT+9)</option>
                  <option value="Asia/Seoul">Seoul (GMT+9)</option>
                </optgroup>
                <optgroup label="Oceania">
                  <option value="Australia/Sydney">Sydney (GMT+10)</option>
                  <option value="Australia/Melbourne">Melbourne (GMT+10)</option>
                  <option value="Australia/Perth">Perth (GMT+8)</option>
                  <option value="Pacific/Auckland">Auckland (GMT+12)</option>
                </optgroup>
                <optgroup label="Latin America & Central America">
                  <option value="America/Mexico_City">Mexico City (GMT-6)</option>
                  <option value="America/Guatemala">Guatemala City (GMT-6)</option>
                  <option value="America/Panama">Panama City (GMT-5)</option>
                  <option value="America/Bogota">Bogota (GMT-5)</option>
                  <option value="America/Lima">Lima (GMT-5)</option>
                  <option value="America/Santiago">Santiago (GMT-4)</option>
                  <option value="America/Sao_Paulo">Sao Paulo (GMT-3)</option>
                  <option value="America/Argentina/Buenos_Aires">Buenos Aires (GMT-3)</option>
                </optgroup>
                <optgroup label="Africa">
                  <option value="Africa/Cairo">Cairo (GMT+3)</option>
                  <option value="Africa/Johannesburg">Johannesburg (GMT+2)</option>
                  <option value="Africa/Nairobi">Nairobi (GMT+3)</option>
                  <option value="Africa/Lagos">Lagos (GMT+1)</option>
                  <option value="Africa/Accra">Accra (GMT+0)</option>
                </optgroup>
              </select>
              <p class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-1 hidden" data-error="timezone"></p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="mastermind-project" class="block text-sm font-body font-medium text-text-secondary mb-2">What are you currently building or exploring?</label>
              <textarea id="mastermind-project" name="current_project" rows="5" maxlength="2000" class="w-full bg-page border border-border-subtle rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-text-primary text-sm placeholder:text-text-muted focus:outline-none focus:border-accent focus:ring-1 focus:ring-accent transition-colors resize-none" placeholder="Share what you're building, testing, or hoping to learn from the mastermind."></textarea>
              <p class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-1 hidden" data-error="current_project"></p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <p class="block text-sm font-body font-medium text-text-secondary mb-3">Would you like to share what you've built in a future session?</p>
                <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page px-4 py-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="wants_to_share" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-border-subtle bg-page text-accent focus:ring-accent">
                  <span>Yes, I’d be open to sharing in a future session</span>
                </label>
              </div>

              <label class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-page px-4 py-4 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                <input type="checkbox" name="consent" required class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 rounded border-border-subtle bg-page text-accent focus:ring-accent">
                <span>I agree to be contacted about the AI Mastermind and understand that my information will be stored for signup and session communication purposes.</span>
              </label>
              <p class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-1 hidden" data-error="consent"></p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4 pt-2">
              <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">
                You will be added to the signup list now. The thank-you page and calendar flow are next.
              </p>
              <button type="submit" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>
                Join the AI Mastermind
              </button>
            </div>

            <div id="mastermind-signup-error" class="hidden rounded-2xl border border-red-400/20 bg-red-400/10 px-5 py-4 text-sm text-red-200"></div>
            <div id="mastermind-signup-success" class="hidden rounded-2xl border border-accent/20 bg-accent/10 px-5 py-4 text-sm text-text-secondary">
              You are on the list.
            </div>
          </form>

          <!--
          <div class="sr-only" aria-hidden="true">
            <div id="mailerlite-mastermind-form" class="ml-embedded" data-form="dYSKh0"></div>
          </div>
          -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="/js/dot-grid.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/nav.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/magnetic.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/tilt.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/mastermind-form.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
